1
00:00:11,240 --> 00:00:12,920
Now you know the truth.

2
00:00:15,480 --> 00:00:16,800
Come with me.

3
00:00:17,640 --> 00:00:18,920
Don't believe him.

4
00:00:21,640 --> 00:00:23,240
Am I wrong?

5
00:00:23,680 --> 00:00:25,240
You've said so much,

6
00:00:25,720 --> 00:00:27,200
but you forgot one thing.

7
00:00:27,800 --> 00:00:30,600
You were the one who gave the elixir manual to Ayun.

8
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:33,200
How could Gu Licheng and his wife know about it?

9
00:00:35,760 --> 00:00:36,760
It was you.

10
00:00:39,160 --> 00:00:41,560
You were the one who sent them to hunt me down

11
00:00:41,800 --> 00:00:46,060
so that we'd fall into your trap to seize the position of Minister of Revenue.

12
00:00:47,160 --> 00:00:49,680
Someone who wouldn't hesitate to hurt his beloved

13
00:00:49,680 --> 00:00:51,610
to seek his own selfish interests,

14
00:00:52,320 --> 00:00:54,160
why does he deserve her love?

15
00:00:55,040 --> 00:00:57,320
And why do you?

16
00:00:57,320 --> 00:00:59,980
Because I'm willing to protect her with my life.

17
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:06,880
Ayun,

18
00:01:07,600 --> 00:01:09,160
I've lied to you for so long.

19
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:12,920
I don't expect you to forgive me,

20
00:01:14,320 --> 00:01:16,200
nor do I expect to have your love.

21
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:19,880
But today,

22
00:01:20,960 --> 00:01:22,240
as his shadow,

23
00:01:23,880 --> 00:01:25,440
even if it costs my life,

24
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:29,280
I will protect you.

25
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:37,039
After all this,

26
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:39,920
are you still going to choose him?

27
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,720
He's just my shadow.

28
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:46,800
He's not anyone's shadow.

29
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:50,560
He is the one who understands, protects, and loves me.

30
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:54,610
I don't care if he's the real Gu Chengyu or not.

31
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,800
In my heart,

32
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,840
he is my Ayu.

33
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,720
Since you won't choose,

34
00:02:06,320 --> 00:02:07,680
I'll choose for you.

35
00:02:17,760 --> 00:02:18,280
A'yu.

36
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:43,880
Go.

37
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:49,090
Taking medicine for severe injuries.

38
00:02:49,440 --> 00:02:50,280
You're dead.

39
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:15,760
Greetings, God of War.

40
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:19,200
Deploy the imperial guards and seal the nine gates.

41
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:20,160
Yes.

42
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:23,840
My shadow.

43
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:25,680
I want you to know that

44
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,240
even if you risk your life,

45
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:29,640
you can't take my woman away.

46
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:41,690
The injury worsened the backlash of the pill.

47
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:42,960
This won't work.

48
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:44,880
I need to find a doctor to treat you.

49
00:03:44,880 --> 00:03:46,680
Don't, don't go out.

50
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:50,660
The imperial guards are all outside.

51
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:53,280
I don't want you to take risks for me.

52
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:55,340
If you don't get treated, you'll die.

53
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:57,840
I'm an orphan.

54
00:03:58,800 --> 00:04:01,520
Ever since the day I was chosen as a shadow,

55
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,280
I was already dead.

56
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,120
I have no name,

57
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:09,160
no past, and no future.

58
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:11,880
It was you

59
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,820
who gave me ten years of happiness

60
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:18,560
and made me understand the meaning of life.

61
00:04:19,839 --> 00:04:20,720
So,

62
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:23,840
to be able to die for you...

63
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:26,120
I am willing.

64
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:30,240
I just need you to promise me one thing.

65
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:31,920
Even if I die,

66
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:35,960
you must live on well.

67
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,120
Promise me.

68
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:57,840
Okay.

69
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,760
I'm sorry.

70
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:18,240
Without you,

71
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:21,100
I wouldn't live alone either.

72
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:37,240
Let me go.

73
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:38,800
Why are you arresting me?

74
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:41,730
The God of War has ordered all doctors to be arrested.

75
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:49,520
I didn't expect Su Cheng to be so vicious.

76
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:50,920
He actually beat me to it.

77
00:05:51,159 --> 00:05:52,760
He insists on wiping me out.

78
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:54,840
Stop running!

79
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:12,850
Let's see where you can run.

80
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,640
You, follow me.

81
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:19,840
Doctor.

82
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:23,080
Mo Yu.

83
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:26,000
Doctor, please, you must cure him.

84
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,040
A doctor has a benevolent heart.

85
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:28,240
I will do my best.

86
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:36,520
Mu Jiuyun.

87
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,560
Didn't expect

88
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:40,400
you'd fall into my hands?

89
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:42,040
You killed my husband.

90
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,320
Today,

91
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:46,330
I want you to pay with your life.

92
00:06:58,440 --> 00:06:59,720
Why are you doing this?

93
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:03,320
In your eyes, she's a life.

94
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:05,000
But in my eyes,

95
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,720
she's just a pawn

96
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:08,720
to prove that only I can protect you.

97
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:10,640
You're a madman.

98
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:13,000
Even if I'm a madman,

99
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:15,360
I mean you no harm.

100
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:17,020
I just want you to come with me.

101
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:18,880
I'd rather die than go with you.

102
00:07:19,320 --> 00:07:21,080
What did I do wrong?

103
00:07:21,440 --> 00:07:23,280
I avenged your blood feud

104
00:07:23,280 --> 00:07:25,160
and protected you when you were in danger.

105
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:27,400
Doesn't that prove my love for you?

106
00:07:27,760 --> 00:07:29,200
In the name of loving me,

107
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:32,240
you killed so many innocent people.

108
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,700
I don't deserve your love.

109
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:37,920
Mo Yu.

110
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:39,600
You don't love me.

111
00:07:39,880 --> 00:07:41,440
I won't force you.

112
00:07:42,400 --> 00:07:44,120
But if you don't come with me,

113
00:07:45,159 --> 00:07:46,760
Mo Yu will die.

114
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:54,040
I will go with you.

115
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:57,400
But you must guarantee he lives.

116
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:06,360
This medicine is enough to save his life.

117
00:08:08,400 --> 00:08:09,800
Are you satisfied now?

118
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,600
Ayun,

119
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,520
don't.

120
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:26,580
Baorui.

121
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,530
Zhong Xiaqiang.

122
00:08:31,840 --> 00:08:33,159
Zijian Qiangqipin, Pengyin.

123
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:33,890
Quan Xuhang.

124
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:34,799
Quan Yulong.

125
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:35,530
Quan Yulong.

126
00:08:35,559 --> 00:08:36,419
Licheng Lefei.

127
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,980
Yunlong Yinyu Jiaguangjing.

128
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:41,640
Luoxiao Conglin Xunbo.
